---
title: Seared Pork Tenderloin with Applesauce and Roasted Green Beans
description: Raise your hand if you’ve tasted a better pairing than pork and apples. Yeah, we thought so. There’s just something about this family-friendly, sweet-and-savory combination that keeps us coming back again and again. In this recipe, homemade applesauce pairs with juicy seared pork chops and a side of roasted green beans for a meal that’ll make the entire family smile.
